        "sender_full_name": "Jake Goulding",
        "timestamp": 1591722402
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>copy propagation would do that opportunistically</p>",
        "id": 200264705,
        "sender_full_name": "oli",
        "timestamp": 1591724238
